    <section name="Using Features">
      <p>To use an above feature in your gadget, you need to specify the feature as
        <i>&lt;require/&gt;</i> in <i>&lt;ModulePrefs/&gt;</i> and defining some Javascript codes to use it. Refer to the
        <a href="../../shindig-1.1.x/shindig-features/jsdoc/index.html">JavascriptDoc for 1.1.x</a> to write your own Javascript.</p>
      <p>For example, if you plan to use the
        <a href="http://svn.apache.org/repos/asf/incubator/shindig/trunk/features/src/main/javascript/features/tabs/feature.xml">tabs/feature.xml</a>,
        your gadget will look like the following:</p>
      <macro name="snippet">
        <param name="id" value="TabExample"/>
        <param name="url" value="file:///D:/java/apache.org/incubator/shindig/trunk/site/src/site/resources/developers/features/simpletab.xml"/>
      </macro>
      <p>You could test your code using the Gadget testing container at:
        <a href="http://localhost:8080/gadgets/files/samplecontainer/samplecontainer.html">http://localhost:8080/gadgets/files/samplecontainer/samplecontainer.html</a></p>
      <img src="../../images/samples/tab.png" alt="Tab Example"/>
    </section>

